冷链业务
<div class="fcbg index-detail">
<div class="bussiesnew">
<div class="dis-min short-text">
<h3>全资冷链物流公司</h3>
<h5>优通全额注资上海津沛冷链物流有限公司，为客户<span class="orangetext">提供专业冷藏食品运输和冷藏食品现代化仓储服务</span>，在冷链管理方面具备丰富的经验和专业知识。</h5>
</div>
<div class="dis-min long-img"><img src="http://www.utscchina.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/index-ll01.png" alt="" width="1100" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-196" /></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="index-detail">
<div class="bussiesnew">
<div class="dis-min long-img"><img src="http://www.utscchina.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/index-ll02.png" alt="" width="1100" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-197" /></div>
<div class="dis-min short-text">
<h3>先进的绿色冷链仓库</h3>
<h5>冷链仓库配备进口林德高位铲车，铲道仅1.5米，库内空间高利用，<span class="orangetext">存储能力达80000吨</span>，引进了先进的<span class="orangetext">无毒害</span>载冷剂制冷技术，确保食品的卫生安全，真正推进绿色物流，高效物流和安全物流。</h5>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="fcbg index-detail">
<div class="bussiesnew">
<div class="dis-min short-text">
<h3>云端把控全程温度</h3>
<h5>依托 <span class="orangetext">“云温控供应链系统”</span>，把大数据信息、物联网技术的优势紧密集合，<span class="orangetext">利用云端进行温度全程控制</span>，保证运输过程中的安全与时效。</h5>
</div>
<div class="dis-min long-img"><img src="http://www.utscchina.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/index-ll03.png" alt="" width="1100" height="800" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-198" /></div>
